						<p>Services are provided under separate written agreements that outline:</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Scope of work and deliverables</li>
							<li>Project timelines and milestones</li>
							<li>Pricing and payment terms</li>
							<li>Intellectual property ownership</li>
							<li>Confidentiality obligations</li>
							<li>Warranties and limitations</li>
						</ul>
						<p>In case of conflict between these Terms of Service and a specific service agreement, the service agreement shall take precedence.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="legal-section">
						<h2 class="text-lg">Payment Terms</h2>
						<p>Unless otherwise specified in a service agreement:</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Invoices are due within 30 days of issue</li>
							<li>Late payments may incur interest charges</li>
							<li>We reserve the right to suspend services for non-payment</li>
							<li>All fees are in Canadian dollars unless otherwise stated</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="legal-section">
						<h2 class="text-lg">Confidentiality</h2>
						<p>We understand that client data and business information are confidential. We commit to:</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Maintaining strict confidentiality of all client information</li>
							<li>Using client data only for agreed-upon purposes</li>
							<li>Implementing appropriate security measures</li>
							<li>Not disclosing client information to third parties without consent</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Specific confidentiality terms will be outlined in individual service agreements or non-disclosure agreements.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="legal-section">
