						<p>If any provision of these Terms of Service is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="legal-section">
						<h2 class="text-lg">Contact Information</h2>
						<p>If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
						<ul class="contact-list">
							<li><strong>Email:</strong> info@getrapidinsights.com</li>
							<li><strong>Address:</strong> 192 Spainda Ave., Toronto ON M5T 2C2, Canada</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<Footer />
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
.legal-page {
	padding-top: 150px;
	padding-bottom: 50px;
}

.legal-content {
	padding: 0 20px;
}

.legal-content h1 {
	margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.last-updated {
	color: #666;
	margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.legal-section {
	margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.legal-section h2 {
	margin-top: 30px;
	margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.legal-section h3 {
	margin-top: 25px;
	margin-bottom: 15px;
	font-weight: 500;
}

.legal-section p {
	margin-bottom: 15px;
	line-height: 1.7;
}

.legal-section ul,
.legal-section ol {
	list-style-position: inside;
	padding-left: 20px;
	margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.legal-section ul {
	list-style-type: disc;
}

.legal-section li {
	margin-bottom: 10px;
	line-height: 1.6;
}

.contact-list {
	list-style-type: none;
	padding-left: 0;
}

.contact-list li {
	margin-bottom: 8px;
}

@media (max-width: 700px) {
	.legal-page {
		padding-top: 120px;
	}

	.legal-content {
		padding: 0 15px;
	}
}
</style>
